config BR2_PACKAGE_UVC_GADGET
	bool "uvc-gadget"
	help
	  Userspace UVC gadget daemon (wlhe fork): pumps MJPEG/YUYV frames into
	  a configfs f_uvc gadget and answers the UVC control events
	  (probe/commit/streamon), so a USB host sees a working webcam. Has a
	  built-in dummy/test-pattern mode (-d) and can take MJPEG from a file
	  (-i) or a V4L2 capture device (-v). We use it because GStreamer's
	  uvcsink won't negotiate our hand-built configfs gadget.

	  https://github.com/wlhe/uvc-gadget
